description.en: Symbol of Erranapogar family. Aenn takes care of it, as the last of his family.

description.br: Símbolo da família Erranapogar. Aenn cuida dele como o último de sua família.
description.cns: 艾诺家族的象征，为唯一活着的艾诺所持有着。
description.de: (Jobquestitem) Zeichen von Erranapogar, der Familie von Aenn. Aenn schätzt dieses sehr, da sie die einzige Überlebende des Familienmassakers ist.
description.fi: Symbol of Erranapogar family. Aenn takes care of it, as the last of his family.

description.fr: symbole de la famille de Aenn, les Erranapogar. Aenn le garde précieusement, elle est l'unique survivante du massacre de sa famille.
description.id: Simbol keluarga Erranapogar. Aenn merawatnya, sebagai yang terakhir dari keluarganya.
description.it: Symbol of Erranapogar family. Aenn takes care of it, as the last of his family.
description.jp: エーエンヌの一族の家紋。忌まわしい一族虐殺事件の時、唯一生き残ったエーエンヌが、この家紋に一族再興を誓ったといわれる。「いかなる苦難にあっても、我は我が望みを捨てじ。待て、しかして希望せよ」
description.kr: 에이엔느의 가문인 에르아나포가의 상징. 가문 대 학살 사건 시 유일하게 살아남은 에이엔느가 가문을 다시 일으켜 세우겠다는 의지로서 소중히 간직하고 있었던 문장.
description.nl: Symbol of Erranapogar family. Aenn takes care of it, as the last of his family.

description.sp: Símbolo de la familia Erranapogar. Aenn se encarga de él, como el último de su familia.
description.sw: Symbol of Erranapogar family. Aenn takes care of it, as the last of his family.
description.th: สัญลักษณ์ของตระกูลเออร์รานาโปการ์ เอิร์นดูแลมันเหมือนคนสุดท้ายของครอบครัว
description.tw: 艾恩家族的象徵，作為家族最後一名存活者的艾恩所持有著
description.vi: Biểu tượng của gia đình Erranapogar. Aenn chăm sóc nó, như là người cuối cùng của gia đình mình.
